[[iftags +版式]]
[[module CSS]]
@import url('https://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/theme%3A3law/1');
[[/module]]

这是为[[[third-law-hub|第三定律]]]设定所作的版式变体，使用该版式需求引入基础的第三定律版式。若需使用该版式，请将以下代码复制到任何页面上：

> @@[[include :scp-wiki-cn:theme:3law]]@@
> @@[[include :scp-wiki-cn:theme:3law-pride]]@@

[[code type="css"]]
/*
    Third Law Canon Pride Theme Variant
    [2021 Wikidot Theme Component]
    Created by GreenWolf.
    The Prometheus Labs/Third Law Flame Logo was created by GreenWolf and is licensed under CC-BY-SA 3.0.
*/

/* HEADER */
#header {
    background-image: url('https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/theme%3A3law-pride/PL_3Law_Logo_Pride_Gradient3.png');
}

#header h2 span::before {
    content: '搞基就罪，快乐就对';
}
[[/code]]
[[/iftags]]

[[module CSS]]
@import url('https://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/theme%3A3law-pride/1');
[[/module]]
